03:37.474 --> 03:54.233
and the new position that establishes for us, or is established for us in Christ, a spiritual position, and briefly we'll think a bit about how that helps us.

03:56.355 --> 04:01.801
And of course, as I speak to you, this word was written to Christians.

04:01.921 --> 04:06.066
