chiefly is to see family and if you go that route on the interstate it takes you right through Effingham, Illinois where I used a credit card to pay for a hotel room for the night and years later a credit report said I was delinquent on a bill to a cell phone company for a purchase made in Effingham.

07:14.757 --> 07:19.564
