08:29.730 --> 08:56.306
happens among Christians, and in the church, and it's been happening a long time, many Christians discover that someone has stolen from them their true Christian identity, or they found that other Christians have had their Christian identity, as it were, stolen from them, or they realize they've never really understood the identity that they have as a Christian, or that

